Key clinical symptoms: In order to predict results and complications in the treatment of COPID-19, consideration should be given to data from chest X-rays and the development of clinical symptoms over time.
The use of steroids: as described above, steroids are an immunosuppressor widely used in infectious diseases as additional therapy to reduce the severity of the inflammatory process.
